Manage Parameters

You can edit parameters to make minor adjustments or change for a different use, and delete them when theyâ€™re no longer needed.

Create and Edit Analytics Dashboards
Edit a parameter:
	* Edit a component and click Advanced Editor.
	* Click the Parameters tab.
	* Click a parameter and add your changes .
	* Click Update.
	* Click Save when complete.
Delete a parameter:
	* Edit a component and click Advanced Editor.
	* Click the Parameters tab.
	* Select a parameter and click Delete.
	* Click Save when complete.
